## What's Been Built

- **FastAPI backend** with 9 API endpoints:
  - /api/health, /api/me (auth)
  - /api/jobs/runs, /api/jobs (system.lakeflow)
  - /api/billing/usage, /api/billing/by-job (system.billing)
  - /api/jobs-api/list, /api/jobs-api/runs/{job_id}, /api/jobs-api/active (Jobs API)

- **React frontend** scaffold with dashboard

- **Databricks config** (databricks.yml, app.yaml with OAuth scopes)

